Class Moment

java.lang.Object
io.github.ethanlamtt.vietchrono.astro.Moment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Moment>
public final class Moment extends Object implements Comparable<Moment>
Represents for astronomical moment.

This class works as an Instant in java.time, it holds the number of seconds from Unix epoch, and it can be converted to JulianDay for astronomical calculations and to Instant for calendrical events. Using this class for almost astronomical API contracts.

This class is immutable and thread-safe.

Since:
1.0.0
